,"target":"recwofVaBASTvL8lL","label":"event"},{"source":"rec3JYCsuVp3qy6br","target":"recJOhn4C4yKIJmvH","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec6RuzA64NK8JjMl","ref":"Exod.2.1","text":"And there went a man of the house of Levi, and took to wife a daughter of Levi.","year":-1572},{"id":"receOudPCMBNqlsjM","ref":"Exod.2.2","text":"And the woman conceived, and bare a son: and when she saw him that he was a goodly child, she hid him three months.","year":-1571},{"id":"recHXlIoZy0EPMNG7","ref":"Exod.2.3","text":"And when she could not longer hide him, she took for him an ark of bulrushes, and daubed it with slime and with pitch, and put the child therein; and she laid it in the flags by the river’s brink.","year":-1571},{"id":"recvbqNINczmSS4zQ","ref":"Exod.2.4","text":"And his sister stood afar off, to wit what would be done to him.","year":-1571},{"id":"recbShm5J204yZ9qw","ref":"Exod.2.5","text":"And the daughter of Pharaoh came down to wash herself at the river; and her maidens walked along by the river’s side; and when she saw the ark among the flags, she sent her maid to fetch it.","year":-1571},{"id":"recc5oQqDlAeUhemC","ref":"Exod.2.6","text":"And when she had opened it, she saw the child: and, behold, the babe wept. And she had compassion on him, and said, This is one of the Hebrews’ children.","year":-1571},{"id":"recZfxEfcuR55rk9h","ref":"Exod.2.7","text":"Then said his sister to Pharaoh’s daughter, Shall I go and call to thee a nurse of the Hebrew women, that she may nurse the child for thee?","year":-1571},{"id":"recDXqHf7lhWOOQDJ","ref":"Exod.2.8","text":"And Pharaoh’s daughter said to her, Go. And the maid went and called the child’s mother.","year":-1571}]}
